WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 17]

02:53.320 --> 02:55.170
If we are going to talk, then let's set things straight.

02:55.200 --> 02:56.430
What's the point of leaving it unclear?

02:56.610 --> 02:57.260
Fine.

02:57.800 --> 02:58.840
Let's talk about

02:58.870 --> 02:59.870
that Lanling Eternal of yours.

03:00.200 --> 03:01.270
He went missing after

03:01.290 --> 03:02.380
that fight in Outlanders' City.

03:02.410 --> 03:04.330
And now, he suddenly appeared in the Fox Clan.

03:04.350 --> 03:05.500
Where's your brain, Bai Shuo?

03:05.530 --> 03:07.030
Don't you think there's something wrong with him?

03:07.050 --> 03:08.920
What could be wrong with Chong Zhao?

03:08.950 --> 03:09.710
He treats me

03:09.730 --> 03:11.570
the same way you treat Tian Huo and Cang Shan.

03:11.600 --> 03:12.980
He has no intention to hurt anyone.

03:13.000 --> 03:15.110
But I won't go hugging Cang Shan.

03:16.579 --> 03:18.450
You wouldn't turn a blind eye if Cang Shang was ever in trouble.

03:18.490 --> 03:20.060
Now that something's up with Chong Zhao,

03:20.090 --> 03:21.320
I was just comforting him.

03:21.350 --> 03:22.160
What's wrong with that?

03:22.180 --> 03:22.810
Yes.

03:23.370 --> 03:24.280
You did nothing wrong.

03:24.560 --> 03:25.470
Then why are you...

03:25.470 --> 03:27.060
You two are childhood sweethearts.

03:27.210 --> 03:29.090
If it weren't for the Contemplation Stone,

03:29.150 --> 03:31.070
we wouldn't even stand a chance to meet.

03:34.040 --> 03:35.350
So when I get the Weak Water Stone,

03:35.380 --> 03:36.270
I'll give it to you

03:36.710 --> 03:38.270
and we shall be considered even.

03:41.880 --> 03:42.970
What did you say?

03:59.900 --> 04:01.610
Since you want to call it even,

04:01.850 --> 04:02.780
fine.

04:02.800 --> 04:04.600
The Weak Water Stone is meant to save my life.

04:04.630 --> 04:06.730
I am responsible for my own life,

04:06.760 --> 04:08.300
so I’ll find it myself.

04:08.680 --> 04:10.850
There's no need to bother you, Master of Bright Moon.

04:14.680 --> 04:17.990
♫Across thousands of miles♫

04:22.910 --> 04:27.780
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

04:37.040 --> 04:37.680
Ah Huo!

04:39.150 --> 04:40.620
Why are you wandering around here?

04:41.390 --> 04:42.740
Auntie has agreed to our marriage.

04:42.800 --> 04:43.570
Come back with me.

04:43.590 --> 04:44.620
You came at the right time.

04:44.650 --> 04:45.550
Mu Jiu,

04:45.580 --> 04:47.310
you grew up in the Fox Clan.

04:47.330 --> 04:49.180
Have you ever seen...

04:49.210 --> 04:51.360
a tall, towering tree that eats humans?

04:51.710 --> 04:53.630
A tree that eats humans?

04:54.870 --> 04:57.170
How could there be such evil thing in Jingyou Mountain?

04:58.140 --> 04:59.370
But...

04:59.400 --> 05:01.020
a tall, towering tree?

05:01.280 --> 05:02.490
I actually do know one.

05:07.550 --> 05:08.900
Is this the giant tree

05:08.930 --> 05:09.880
you were talking about?

05:10.120 --> 05:10.750
Yes.

05:11.080 --> 05:12.250
It's called the Emotion Tree.

05:12.980 --> 05:15.230
You know that we Fox Clan practice curses, right?

05:15.290 --> 05:16.940
The source of cursed power is from

05:16.970 --> 05:18.530
the emotional vein within our bodies.

05:19.590 --> 05:21.230
When a newborn fox

05:21.260 --> 05:22.850
receives blessings from the Emotion Tree,

05:22.880 --> 05:24.850
the emotional vein will grow inside its body.

05:25.290 --> 05:26.210
So this tree

05:26.240 --> 05:28.030
is the foundation of our Fox Clan.

05:28.050 --> 05:30.330
It's definitely not the man-eating tree you're looking for.

05:51.400 --> 05:52.480
Look at me.

05:52.890 --> 05:53.740
Why?

05:54.409 --> 05:56.220
Because the Emotion Tree can feel love.

05:56.520 --> 05:57.840
If love fills your heart as you look at me,

05:57.860 --> 05:59.630
a single touch of the Emotion Tree

05:59.659 --> 06:01.110
will make it bloom with flowers.

06:04.520 --> 06:05.520
Try it again.

06:12.250 --> 06:13.000
That's lame.

06:13.030 --> 06:14.150
I'm not interested.

06:14.670 --> 06:15.870
Let me try it instead.

06:31.810 --> 06:32.930
What's going on?

06:33.110 --> 06:34.480
Why is there no response?

06:34.909 --> 06:36.620
My aunt told me when I was little.

06:42.050 --> 06:43.000
There's no need to try.

06:43.580 --> 06:44.750
Whether you like me or not

06:44.780 --> 06:46.070
has nothing to do with me.

06:46.190 --> 06:47.800
I need to find the tree that eats humans.

06:47.830 --> 06:48.590
Goodbye.

06:48.940 --> 06:49.690
No.

06:50.230 --> 06:51.280
Wait!

06:51.350 --> 06:52.030
Trust me.

06:52.060 --> 06:53.210
I really like you.

06:53.230 --> 06:55.040
This tree is old and useless.

06:55.860 --> 06:56.690
Huo.

06:57.330 --> 06:58.680
You can't believe that.

06:59.720 --> 07:00.750
Huo!

07:19.640 --> 07:21.500
The love tree of the Fox Clan?

07:22.010 --> 07:24.120
That's just ridiculous.

07:25.280 --> 07:26.160
Fu Ling.

07:31.400 --> 07:32.390
Come here.

08:00.570 --> 08:02.420
Mu Jiu was here with Tian Huo just now.

08:02.610 --> 08:04.660
The Emotion Tree did not bewitch or attack them,

08:04.690 --> 08:05.970
but it's attacking me.

08:06.040 --> 08:07.070
Why?

08:07.860 --> 08:08.790
Is it because...

08:09.340 --> 08:10.950
I'm not from the Fox Clan?

08:19.740 --> 08:20.710
Greetings, Master.

08:23.290 --> 08:24.490
Are you...

08:25.230 --> 08:26.630
Looking for Tian Huo?

08:35.730 --> 08:36.980
According to the rules of the Fox Clan,

08:37.260 --> 08:38.620
it's inauspicious for anyone

08:38.650 --> 08:40.210
but the bride to touch the wedding dress.

08:42.320 --> 08:43.549
This wedding dress

08:43.549 --> 08:45.040
looks quite dated.

08:45.070 --> 08:47.080
Was this what you wore when you got married back then?

08:48.000 --> 08:49.850
Marriage is not in my destiny.

08:50.570 --> 08:52.480
This was left behind by my sister.

08:53.630 --> 08:56.030
It's the most important thing to me.

08:56.400 --> 08:57.970
Is your sister...

08:58.000 --> 09:00.080
the legendary Saintess Ling Long?

09:03.000 --> 09:04.500
How do you know Ling Long?

09:04.900 --> 09:06.140
Because I know

09:06.160 --> 09:07.130
you're Wu.

09:10.430 --> 09:13.380
Ms. Bai, you actually know my childhood name?

09:13.410 --> 09:14.930
Didn't Mu Jiu tell you?

09:15.000 --> 09:16.000
When we were in Outlanders' City,

09:16.020 --> 09:17.590
our group happened to find ourselves

09:17.610 --> 09:19.850
in the realm of illusion that formed from the lingering resentment of

09:19.880 --> 09:21.390
Kunlun's Mr. Rong Xian after his death.

09:22.240 --> 09:24.120
We witnessed what happened between Saintess Ling Long

09:24.120 --> 09:25.790
and Mr. Rong Xian,

09:26.150 --> 09:27.870
as well as the tragedy back then.

09:28.060 --> 09:29.300
In the realm of resentment,

09:29.330 --> 09:30.610
the role I played

09:30.630 --> 09:32.040
happened to be you, Wu.

09:33.380 --> 09:34.610
I've seen

09:34.780 --> 09:35.590
this earring before.

09:39.910 --> 09:40.870
It's been a thousand years.

09:40.870 --> 09:42.550
I didn't expect someone to mention

09:44.110 --> 09:45.800
that scoundrel Rong Xian.

09:45.820 --> 09:47.610
He even has the nerve to remember my sister?

09:47.850 --> 09:50.600
My entire clan here at Jingyou Mountain was almost destroyed by him.

09:51.050 --> 09:52.720
My sister's passionate love

09:52.740 --> 09:54.030
ended in hatred.

09:54.340 --> 09:57.060
In the end, she ended up dead with her soul completely obliterated.

09:57.360 --> 10:00.160
But yet, there's still a wisp of his memory that continues to exist in this world.

10:00.180 --> 10:01.680
How ridiculous!

10:01.700 --> 10:02.830
Please calm down.

10:02.860 --> 10:04.970
There's actually another truth behind what happened back then.

10:05.090 --> 10:07.560
Mr. Rong Xian was also victimized by someone from Kunlun.

10:07.590 --> 10:08.720
That’s why he made that big mistake.

10:08.750 --> 10:10.120
He was truly wholehearted

10:10.120 --> 10:11.120
towards Saintess Ling Long.

10:11.150 --> 10:12.030
Ms. Bai.

10:13.050 --> 10:16.000
Ultimately, this matter is a family affair of Jingyou Mountain.

10:16.120 --> 10:18.340
What do you mean by meddling

10:18.620 --> 10:19.770
and commenting so much?

10:20.450 --> 10:21.400
I'm sorry.

10:21.420 --> 10:22.780
I didn’t mean to.

10:23.580 --> 10:25.700
It was simply that, by chance,

10:25.730 --> 10:27.770
I learned some of the truth.

10:27.790 --> 10:29.360
I know it's one of your personal grudges.

10:29.390 --> 10:29.700
That's why...

10:29.720 --> 10:30.600
No need.

10:31.060 --> 10:33.040
The deceased has passed away for a thousand years.

10:33.260 --> 10:34.690
Why bring up the past again?

10:46.950 --> 10:50.210
Could I trouble you take this back to Tian Huo?

10:50.290 --> 10:51.510
Consider it as a wedding gift to them

10:51.510 --> 10:53.030
from me as their aunt.

10:53.140 --> 10:54.020
Please.

10:55.280 --> 10:56.070
Master.

10:57.280 --> 10:58.130
Master.

10:58.150 --> 10:59.150
I need to talk to you.

11:01.910 --> 11:02.550
Master.

11:05.240 --> 11:07.100
Didn't you see that we have a guest?

11:07.120 --> 11:08.900
Get out of here now!

11:09.380 --> 11:10.740
I'm here to report something to you.

11:11.120 --> 11:13.040
That matter has been taken care of.

11:13.060 --> 11:14.610
No one is discussing it anymore.

11:14.640 --> 11:16.290
But I don't know for how long more

11:16.310 --> 11:17.070
can we suppress it.

11:17.560 --> 11:19.130
So please, Master,

11:19.150 --> 11:20.100
make a decision quickly.

11:20.120 --> 11:22.360
I’ll tell you one last time.

11:22.390 --> 11:24.100
I will take care of that matter myself.

11:24.150 --> 11:24.840
Get out!

11:39.060 --> 11:40.340
Elder Chang Sheng!

11:40.370 --> 11:41.440
Please wait.

11:42.140 --> 11:43.490
I have something to ask.

11:43.510 --> 11:44.710
You are just a brat from the Human Race.

11:44.740 --> 11:46.260
If you have any questions, go and ask Master of Bright Moon.

11:46.280 --> 11:47.250
I don’t have time for you.

11:47.280 --> 11:49.390
I see that you are a man of character,

11:50.090 --> 11:51.280
and is straightforward

11:51.320 --> 11:52.470
and bold.

11:52.770 --> 11:54.130
I wonder if you were the guard Ba,

11:54.200 --> 11:55.850
who served beside the Master a thousand years ago?

11:57.600 --> 11:58.930
You're not Ba?

11:59.050 --> 12:00.530
Then, are you Qi?

12:00.560 --> 12:01.770
I don't know who are

12:01.790 --> 12:02.790
these people.

12:02.820 --> 12:04.300
I'm only 300 years old.

12:04.320 --> 12:06.120
How could I know what happened a thousand years ago?

12:06.150 --> 12:07.570
Only 300 years old?

12:08.080 --> 12:09.000
So you wouldn't have experienced

12:09.030 --> 12:10.910
what happened to Rong Xian and Ling Long a thousand years ago.

12:11.590 --> 12:13.890
Then how did you become an Elder of the Fox Clan?

12:14.110 --> 12:15.620
That scoundrel Rong Xian

12:15.670 --> 12:16.980
almost wiped out

12:17.010 --> 12:19.070
the entire Fox Clan a thousand years ago.

12:19.260 --> 12:20.340
Those who fought

12:20.360 --> 12:23.290
have almost all died in that battle.

12:23.630 --> 12:25.080
If there was anyone else in the clan,

12:25.100 --> 12:26.450
do you think I'd want to be stuck with

12:26.480 --> 12:27.960
this unlucky position as an Elder?

12:28.190 --> 12:29.290
Shoo, go away.

12:29.790 --> 12:31.220
Don't get in the way of my work.

12:36.000 --> 12:37.430
In that realm of resentment,

12:37.450 --> 12:38.880
Ling Long once said that

12:38.910 --> 12:40.830
the guard, Ba, was easily irritable.

12:41.060 --> 12:42.490
If it isn't Chang Sheng,

12:42.520 --> 12:43.690
who else could it be?

12:44.180 --> 12:44.940
Bai Shuo.

12:44.970 --> 12:46.240
What does this person, Ba,

12:46.260 --> 12:47.900
has anything to do with

12:47.930 --> 12:49.010
what we're doing here?

12:49.740 --> 12:51.460
Today, I noticed a scar on the back of Chang Mei's hand

12:51.490 --> 12:53.300
that looks just like the ones you had.

12:53.320 --> 12:54.360
That means,

12:54.390 --> 12:56.060
if she wasn't the one who attacked you,

12:56.080 --> 12:57.620
she would at least know who was it.

12:57.920 --> 12:59.250
Does that make Chang Mei a bad person?

12:59.270 --> 13:00.580
No, I must tell Master about this.

13:00.610 --> 13:01.300
Stop!

13:01.650 --> 13:02.370
Sit down.

13:03.760 --> 13:04.880
Didn't I tell you?

13:04.910 --> 13:05.790
The scene from the Contemplation Stone

13:05.790 --> 13:07.420
suggests that Fan Yue will be in danger.

13:07.440 --> 13:08.800
What we need to do now is to

13:08.830 --> 13:10.830
find the Weak Water Stone with Fan Yue first.

13:10.850 --> 13:12.300
We shouldn't get him involved.

13:15.240 --> 13:17.140
Since when was I on your side?

13:18.070 --> 13:19.280
Our common purpose

13:19.360 --> 13:20.550
is to protect Fan Yue.

13:20.550 --> 13:21.800
So why are we not on the same side?

13:21.870 --> 13:24.080
Are you going to watch him get eaten up by that

13:24.100 --> 13:25.570
strange tree, just like you were?

13:29.270 --> 13:30.920
That kind of makes sense.

13:31.680 --> 13:33.990
The Weak Water Stone is now in Chang Mei's hands.

13:34.010 --> 13:35.410
If we want her to take it out,

13:35.440 --> 13:36.880
we must fully understand her.

13:37.720 --> 13:38.840
I thought resolving her grudge

13:38.840 --> 13:41.010
regarding Ling Long's death would help.

13:41.170 --> 13:43.410
I didn't expect her to react that strongly today.

13:44.490 --> 13:45.580
Chang Mei also said

13:45.610 --> 13:47.100
she isn't destined to be married.

13:47.270 --> 13:48.500
But back then, the guard Qi

13:48.550 --> 13:50.270
was clearly in love with Wu.

13:50.960 --> 13:51.850
What happened

13:51.880 --> 13:53.730
in the last thousand years?

13:53.750 --> 13:56.090
Only by finding Ba can we uncover the truth.

13:58.470 --> 13:59.510
What is this?

14:00.870 --> 14:01.720
This is the wedding gift from Chang Mei

14:01.720 --> 14:03.550
for Tian Huo and Mu Jiu.

14:03.570 --> 14:05.020
I'd like you to take it to them for me.

14:05.050 --> 14:05.770
What?

14:06.050 --> 14:08.260
Tian Huo is going to marry Mu Jiu?

14:08.770 --> 14:10.690
We've searched the entire Fox Clan today.

14:10.940 --> 14:13.270
There's only one giant tree that matches Bai Shuo's description.

14:14.320 --> 14:15.720
There must be something wrong with that Emotion Tree.

14:16.140 --> 14:17.980
But when I was there with Mu Jiu today,

14:18.740 --> 14:20.430
the tree was very quiet.

14:20.450 --> 14:21.780
Nothing seemed strange.

14:21.810 --> 14:23.410
We have no other clues now.

14:24.550 --> 14:26.430
I'll go check it out again at night.

14:26.460 --> 14:27.590
But Master,

14:27.620 --> 14:29.090
your injuries...

14:29.450 --> 14:31.780
How come you're starting to doubt me too?

14:31.820 --> 14:32.650
Master.

14:33.020 --> 14:34.390
I'm just worried.

14:34.410 --> 14:35.530
I'm not doubting you.

14:36.770 --> 14:38.980
I still have two stars out of my Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

14:39.120 --> 14:41.050
It’s far from the end of the world.

14:41.070 --> 14:42.110
Even if I'm injured,

14:42.140 --> 14:43.770
no one can take my life.

14:43.790 --> 14:44.880
Even if you don't die,

14:44.910 --> 14:46.590
it doesn't mean you won't get hurt.

14:46.620 --> 14:48.270
That's what Bai Shuo said.

14:50.430 --> 14:51.310
What?

14:53.780 --> 14:55.340
Why do I feel that

14:55.500 --> 14:57.260
ever since Bai Shuo came to Bright Moon Palace,

14:57.290 --> 14:59.170
both of you have become strange.

14:59.190 --> 15:01.560
You wouldn't have said such things back in the Demon Race.

15:01.630 --> 15:02.880
And there's Cang Shan.

15:03.060 --> 15:05.320
As a demon, he couldn't even take a human away.

15:05.510 --> 15:06.700
How ridiculous!

15:07.300 --> 15:08.850
Not only we have changed,

15:08.880 --> 15:10.690
you have changed too.

15:10.710 --> 15:11.900
I’ve changed?

15:11.930 --> 15:13.290
Previously, you were

15:13.310 --> 15:14.590
only interested in investigating

15:14.620 --> 15:16.160
the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

15:16.290 --> 15:17.810
You stayed steadfast to your goal

15:17.840 --> 15:19.330
no matter how hard things got.

15:19.410 --> 15:20.860
But now, you would even

15:20.890 --> 15:23.050
consider giving up collecting the Contemplations.

15:23.280 --> 15:24.400
Isn't that change?

15:24.420 --> 15:25.120
That's because...

15:25.120 --> 15:26.780
Because you like Bai Shuo.

15:29.960 --> 15:31.400
Because you like her,

15:31.420 --> 15:33.020
her life is more important than yours

15:33.050 --> 15:34.140
in your heart.

15:35.050 --> 15:36.140
But Master,

15:36.330 --> 15:38.930
I'm afraid that's what Bai Shuo thinks too.

15:38.960 --> 15:41.460
Since you both care about each other,

15:41.690 --> 15:43.810
you should take good care of yourselves.

15:44.030 --> 15:45.390
Don't let her worry about you.

15:54.670 --> 15:55.660
I understand.

15:56.760 --> 15:58.080
When I get the Weak Water Stone,

15:59.290 --> 16:00.880
I'll speak to her properly.

16:04.510 --> 16:05.870
Do you like Mu Jiu?

16:08.820 --> 16:10.200
That's how people are.

16:10.470 --> 16:11.740
It's easy to perceive others,

16:11.940 --> 16:12.940
but we remain blind when

16:12.970 --> 16:13.970
reflecting upon ourselves.

16:15.020 --> 16:17.010
The three of us have been together for years.

16:17.400 --> 16:18.510
I also hope

16:18.650 --> 16:20.530
you can let go of your grudges

16:20.670 --> 16:22.600
and find someone you want to spend your life with.

16:32.090 --> 16:33.280
Elder Chang Sheng has given orders to

16:33.320 --> 16:35.080
search carefully as there have been signs of intruders

16:35.160 --> 16:36.250
within the clan today.

16:36.280 --> 16:37.650
Don't let anyone suspicious get away.

16:37.680 --> 16:38.450
Yes.

16:42.180 --> 16:43.220
You brought this on.

16:47.850 --> 16:49.820
I happened to visit the forbidden area of the Fox Clan

16:49.850 --> 16:51.370
and had accidentally made some moves.

16:51.400 --> 16:52.900
That's what left the trail.

16:53.630 --> 16:55.230
Jingyou Mountain is not a place for recklessness.

16:55.250 --> 16:56.770
Please be careful.

16:56.800 --> 16:58.800
If we fail the mission, we won't be able to answer to our master.

16:58.820 --> 16:59.460
Don’t worry.

16:59.490 --> 17:01.420
I've come up with a wonderful plan for you.

17:02.570 --> 17:03.660
What do you want?

17:05.260 --> 17:06.220
I'm warning you.

17:06.619 --> 17:08.069
Capturing Bai Shuo is my mission.

17:09.470 --> 17:10.230
Don't worry.

17:10.260 --> 17:12.099
I won't take your first credit from you.

17:12.119 --> 17:14.109
The Emotion Tree of the Fox Clan will attack any foreign race.

17:14.260 --> 17:16.579
Tonight, I'll lure Fan Yue to the Emotion Tree.

17:16.609 --> 17:18.540
You take the chance to capture Bai Shuo.

17:19.819 --> 17:20.569
Wait!

17:22.740 --> 17:23.480
Who are you?

17:23.730 --> 17:24.849
Catch her!

17:27.310 --> 17:27.960
Hurry!

17:30.130 --> 17:31.090
Catch her!

17:31.700 --> 17:32.410
Stop!

17:32.770 --> 17:33.590
Stop!

17:37.880 --> 17:38.680
Auntie.

17:38.710 --> 17:40.350
I've been busy since I came back,

17:40.370 --> 17:41.810
and it slipped my mind to tell you.

17:41.960 --> 17:43.460
Don't be mad at me.

17:44.090 --> 17:45.120
I'll tell you everything

17:45.180 --> 17:46.750
you want to know.

17:47.220 --> 17:48.130
Forget it.

17:48.700 --> 17:50.860
There's no point talking about the past.

17:53.000 --> 17:54.440
Let me just ask you one thing.

17:55.410 --> 17:56.900
In the realm of resentment,

17:56.930 --> 17:59.040
did you notice Ling Long and Rong Xian’s children?

17:59.570 --> 18:00.440
Yes.

18:00.460 --> 18:02.500
Fan Yue changed the child's fate in the realm of resentment

18:02.530 --> 18:04.420
by saving the foetus in Saintess Ling Long’s womb.

18:04.440 --> 18:05.850
He was severely injured because of that.

18:06.600 --> 18:07.610
But Auntie,

18:07.650 --> 18:09.180
given that the realm of resentment

18:09.210 --> 18:10.490
is not real,

18:10.510 --> 18:12.270
will changing someone's fate inside

18:12.300 --> 18:13.950
actually change reality?

18:14.510 --> 18:16.060
I see.

18:16.280 --> 18:17.650
It was Fan Yue.

18:18.920 --> 18:19.690
Auntie?

18:21.140 --> 18:22.130
Auntie!

18:23.630 --> 18:24.890
I'm fine.

18:25.390 --> 18:26.140
Jiu.

18:26.920 --> 18:28.450
Did Tian Huo and the rest

18:28.470 --> 18:30.620
ask you about the Weak Water Stone?

18:30.650 --> 18:31.690
Yes.

18:31.710 --> 18:33.360
But I don't know what that is.

18:33.390 --> 18:34.830
I even asked around within the clan,

18:34.860 --> 18:36.370
but no one seem to know of it.

18:36.390 --> 18:37.280
Auntie.

18:37.310 --> 18:38.460
Do you know what the Weak Water Stone is?

18:38.480 --> 18:39.330
Jiu.

18:39.460 --> 18:40.730
Listen to me.

18:40.790 --> 18:42.510
You're going to marry Tian Huo tomorrow.

18:42.540 --> 18:44.020
According to our clan's rules,

18:44.070 --> 18:45.870
you shouldn't see each other before that.

18:45.890 --> 18:46.960
Not just Tian Huo,

18:46.990 --> 18:49.000
but also don't meet anyone from Bright Moon Palace either.

18:49.030 --> 18:49.920
Why?

18:49.940 --> 18:51.630
There's no such thing as why.

18:53.980 --> 18:55.680
Anyway, if you want to leave the Fox Clan,

18:55.680 --> 18:57.220
you must listen to me.

18:57.310 --> 18:58.310
Auntie,

18:59.170 --> 19:00.540
are you sick?

19:01.000 --> 19:01.750
Tell me

19:01.770 --> 19:03.130
if there's anything I can do for you.

19:04.030 --> 19:06.180
I just have too much going on these days.

19:06.210 --> 19:07.780
I'm tired.

19:08.210 --> 19:09.340
You can leave now.

19:09.370 --> 19:10.040
By the way,

19:10.120 --> 19:11.620
ask Elder Chang Wu to come over.

19:30.120 --> 19:32.460
Why is Auntie acting weird today?

19:36.920 --> 19:38.480
You sly fox, you pretty boy!

19:38.500 --> 19:39.200
Tell me.

19:39.230 --> 19:40.360
How did you manage to fool Tian Huo?

19:40.380 --> 19:41.690
What nonsense?

19:41.720 --> 19:42.780
What's wrong with you?

19:50.600 --> 19:51.400
Huo.

19:52.260 --> 19:53.130
Look at him.

19:53.160 --> 19:54.900
He punched me without any reason.

19:54.970 --> 19:56.270
At the very least, we've shared

19:56.270 --> 19:57.590
meals and a roof back at Unbridled Pavilion.

19:57.610 --> 19:59.450
You people from the Bright Moon Palace are so disloyal.

19:59.480 --> 20:00.590
Look at his punches.

20:00.730 --> 20:01.690
Nonsense!

20:01.720 --> 20:03.090
It was you, with your slick words,

20:03.110 --> 20:04.120
who tricked Tian Huo.

20:04.140 --> 20:05.640
Otherwise, why would she marry you?

20:05.800 --> 20:06.360
You!

20:06.400 --> 20:07.120
Let go of her!

20:07.200 --> 20:07.960
-Let go!
-Cang Shan.

20:08.450 --> 20:09.490
You misunderstood.

20:09.570 --> 20:11.550
It was my idea to get married.

20:12.770 --> 20:13.530
What?

20:16.090 --> 20:17.090
But...

20:18.600 --> 20:19.730
it's just a fake marriage.

20:20.070 --> 20:21.480
It has nothing to do with love.

20:21.610 --> 20:22.880
It's simply a stopgap measure.

20:23.600 --> 20:24.690
I knew it.

20:24.850 --> 20:26.300
How could you like someone like him?

20:26.320 --> 20:27.040
Still,

20:27.070 --> 20:28.070
no matter the circumstances,

20:28.090 --> 20:29.720
marriage isn't something to be taken lightly, right?

20:29.750 --> 20:30.840
Why not?

20:30.940 --> 20:31.620
Because...

20:33.620 --> 20:35.120
Because marriage is a big deal...

20:36.470 --> 20:38.320
Because marriage is a big deal, you need our master's approval.

20:38.340 --> 20:39.300
In my opinion,

20:39.880 --> 20:41.290
you need our permission to proceed.

20:44.100 --> 20:46.500
Where'd you learn to say all of that, you silly rock?

20:46.520 --> 20:47.240
Your master's approval?

20:47.270 --> 20:48.140
In your opinion?

20:48.190 --> 20:49.520
I think I understand now.

20:49.540 --> 20:50.450
He's trying to take advantage of you,

20:50.480 --> 20:51.610
and wants to claim seniority over you.

21:03.080 --> 21:03.890
Huo.

21:04.340 --> 21:05.420
Cang Shan seems to...

21:05.440 --> 21:06.440
He is just a friend.

21:10.040 --> 21:11.760
Just friends?

21:41.000 --> 21:43.480
Cold Spring Palace clearly doesn't disappoint.

21:43.650 --> 21:45.960
You came all the way here to die.

21:50.290 --> 21:51.090
She's gone this way!

21:51.160 --> 21:51.950
Let’s go!

22:01.570 --> 22:02.370
Elder Wu.

22:02.390 --> 22:03.350
This is the residence of

22:03.380 --> 22:04.790
the lady who was brought here by Master of Bright Moon.

22:04.810 --> 22:06.120
Let's go and have a look regardless.

22:11.560 --> 22:12.790
Elder Wu.

22:12.820 --> 22:14.700
It's late. What's up?

22:14.730 --> 22:15.610
Ms. Bai.

22:15.800 --> 22:17.560
A few intruders broke into the forest.

22:17.860 --> 22:18.730
Many of our clansmen

22:18.760 --> 22:20.110
were injured by them by their demonic techniques.

22:20.280 --> 22:22.070
A thief was seen heading towards your residence.

22:22.150 --> 22:23.680
I wonder if you have seen them?

22:24.530 --> 22:25.180
Miss?

22:27.420 --> 22:28.600
I haven't seen them.

22:28.870 --> 22:29.630
If you

22:29.650 --> 22:30.810
see anyone suspicious,

22:30.850 --> 22:31.950
you just have to shout for help.

22:32.000 --> 22:32.830
Tonight, our clansmen

22:32.830 --> 22:33.830
will be patrolling the forest.

22:34.210 --> 22:35.360
I won't bother you then.

22:35.810 --> 22:36.500
Let's go.

22:43.010 --> 22:44.530
You hurt the Fox Clan?

22:44.560 --> 22:46.150
You wouldn't hurt people for no reason.

22:46.170 --> 22:46.980
So why?

22:47.210 --> 22:47.970
Shuo.

22:48.390 --> 22:50.190
There are many things I can't tell you now.

22:50.210 --> 22:51.220
But trust me.

22:51.260 --> 22:52.860
I have no ill intentions towards you.

22:53.820 --> 22:55.380
While they are searching in the forest,

22:55.400 --> 22:56.640
leave with me now.

22:58.570 --> 22:59.490
I can't leave.

23:00.720 --> 23:01.950
Because of Fan Yue?

23:04.980 --> 23:06.500
He won't be able to control you anymore.

23:06.670 --> 23:08.180
Tonight is a rare opportunity.

23:08.310 --> 23:10.160
If you don't leave, you won't have anymore chances.

23:10.890 --> 23:12.160
You did something to Fan Yue,

23:12.160 --> 23:12.890
didn't you?

23:14.780 --> 23:15.750
Chong Zhao.

23:15.830 --> 23:17.240
What are you hiding from me?

23:17.260 --> 23:19.040
Are you trying to trick me a second time?

23:19.180 --> 23:20.100
It's not me.

23:21.980 --> 23:22.960
It's Fu Ling.

23:23.540 --> 23:25.460
Cold Spring Palace wants to take you back.

23:25.480 --> 23:27.910
Fu Ling has lured Fan Yue to the Emotion Tree.

23:27.940 --> 23:28.980
That place is very strange.

23:29.000 --> 23:30.160
She will definitely be able to stall Fan Yue.

23:30.190 --> 23:31.320
If you don't leave now,

23:31.340 --> 23:32.960
there's bound to be more trouble after this.

23:33.060 --> 23:35.110
I'll send you back to Old Turtle. He'll protect you.

23:35.540 --> 23:36.610
Fan Yue...

23:36.780 --> 23:38.260
went to the Emotion Tree?

23:44.220 --> 23:45.950
Fan Yue and I are companions.

23:46.060 --> 23:47.650
Not to mention that he's in danger right now,

23:47.680 --> 23:49.060
even if nothing happens tonight,

23:49.080 --> 23:51.120
I never thought of leaving him behind.

23:51.150 --> 23:52.460
I'll ask you about your affairs with

23:52.480 --> 23:53.780
Cold Spring Palace when I'm back.

23:55.440 --> 23:56.690
Fan Yue is a demon.

23:56.860 --> 23:58.740
He's only interested in you because of the Contemplation Stone.

23:59.400 --> 24:00.160
Shuo.

24:00.800 --> 24:02.340
Why don't you understand?

24:02.370 --> 24:03.910
In the beginning, perhaps.

24:04.510 --> 24:07.170
But after what happened at Ning'an City, he has been treating me sincerely.

24:07.260 --> 24:09.860
Instead, aren't you the one who has been hiding things from me,

24:10.120 --> 24:11.320
refusing to tell me anything?

24:12.230 --> 24:15.150
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

24:12.780 --> 24:14.650
I'm not the old Bai Shuo anymore.

24:14.680 --> 24:16.960
I won't trust others so easily.

24:15.930 --> 24:18.470
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

24:16.980 --> 24:18.550
Fan Yue may be a demon.

24:18.580 --> 24:19.860
However, as a demon,

24:19.290 --> 24:23.050
♫I remember that word of concern♫

24:19.880 --> 24:21.150
he is better than any Eternal.

24:21.770 --> 24:22.680
Chong Zhao.

24:23.590 --> 24:25.390
Don’t let me down again.

24:23.680 --> 24:26.920
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

24:27.420 --> 24:30.160
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

24:27.840 --> 24:28.630
Let go.

24:30.990 --> 24:34.380
♫It dried in the wind♫

24:35.060 --> 24:36.830
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

24:37.240 --> 24:40.850
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

24:41.890 --> 24:44.980
♫That year, that year♫

24:45.670 --> 24:48.880
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

24:49.500 --> 24:53.010
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

25:04.020 --> 25:05.260
I must find a way to

25:05.280 --> 25:06.850
get him closer to the Emotion Tree.

25:07.230 --> 25:08.750
You came seeking for death,

25:08.780 --> 25:10.760
and even found this tree for me.

25:12.130 --> 25:14.500
Since you saved me from more hassle,

25:14.810 --> 25:16.920
I will reward you by keeping your body intact later.

25:16.940 --> 25:18.620
Thank you for your kindness, Master.

25:18.650 --> 25:19.890
I just wonder

25:19.960 --> 25:21.280
who will die tonight?

25:21.910 --> 25:23.280
You've overestimated yourself.

25:34.640 --> 25:36.440
The Emotion Tree won't attack the Fox Clan,

25:36.460 --> 25:37.940
but it will devour you.

25:37.970 --> 25:39.720
I'm afraid you won't be able

25:39.850 --> 25:41.500
to fulfil that favor today.

25:47.440 --> 25:48.030
Stand up.

25:48.030 --> 25:50.210
How could people from Cold Spring Palace end up here in Jingyou Mountain?

25:50.230 --> 25:51.750
Are you sure you're not mistaken?

25:52.210 --> 25:54.540
Many of the juniors had their tails cut off.

25:54.950 --> 25:56.600
Given the demonic power in their wound,

25:56.680 --> 25:57.640
who else could it have been

25:57.680 --> 25:58.470
besides Cold Spring Palace?

25:58.500 --> 26:01.650
Jingyou Mountain and Zhen Yu has been on good terms.

26:01.870 --> 26:04.070
Why did he send someone to cause trouble suddenly?

26:04.630 --> 26:06.080
It's for the Emotion Tree.

26:06.520 --> 26:07.240
The people from Cold Spring Palace

26:07.270 --> 26:08.970
have set their sights on our Emotion Tree?

26:09.270 --> 26:10.240
Haven't you heard?

26:10.240 --> 26:11.250
The Emotion Tree has gone awry.

26:11.280 --> 26:12.350
Something is definitely wrong.

26:12.370 --> 26:12.970
Yes.

26:13.000 --> 26:14.170
-There must be something wrong.
-Yes.

26:14.200 --> 26:15.310
Shut up!

26:15.800 --> 26:16.750
Chang Wu.

26:17.160 --> 26:18.920
Take the injured back to heal.

26:18.950 --> 26:19.970
Chang Sheng.

26:19.990 --> 26:21.230
Keep searching with your men.

26:21.290 --> 26:22.960
Don't let anyone suspicious go.

26:23.020 --> 26:23.670
Yes.

26:28.080 --> 26:28.800
Let's go.

26:30.610 --> 26:31.460
Master.

26:31.750 --> 26:32.840
Let me stay with you.

26:32.860 --> 26:33.620
It's okay.

26:33.760 --> 26:34.770
Just go.

26:34.960 --> 26:35.740
Yes.

26:42.780 --> 26:44.490
Ms. Bai, you seem to know

26:44.700 --> 26:47.030
more than I thought.

26:47.360 --> 26:48.950
I'm not the one you should be wary of,

26:48.970 --> 26:50.290
but Cold Spring Palace.

26:50.600 --> 26:52.630
Fu Ling is luring Fan Yue to the Emotion Tree.

26:52.650 --> 26:54.680
No matter what their schemes are against Jingyou Mountain,

26:54.700 --> 26:56.260
tonight, you and Fan Yue

26:56.290 --> 26:57.250
should be allies.

26:57.370 --> 26:58.370
How ridiculous.

26:59.240 --> 27:01.520
Cold Spring Palace is targeting Fan Yue.

27:01.540 --> 27:02.870
Now that Fan Yue is in trouble,

27:02.900 --> 27:04.310
that has got nothing to do with me.

27:04.600 --> 27:05.330
Master.

27:05.840 --> 27:08.320
Yesterday, I told you about what happened inside Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

27:08.340 --> 27:09.450
you should have believed that

27:09.480 --> 27:11.640
Fan Yue and I have no ill intentions towards Jingyou Mountain.

27:11.850 --> 27:13.490
Just now, I heard your clansmen saying that

27:13.510 --> 27:15.350
something is wrong with Emotion Tree.

27:15.380 --> 27:16.900
If Cold Spring Palace finds out about this,

27:16.920 --> 27:18.750
the Fox Clan will be in danger.

27:18.960 --> 27:21.090
I ask that you please take me to the Emotion Tree.

27:21.120 --> 27:22.150
As for all other matters,

27:22.170 --> 27:23.460
I will handle it myself.

27:26.240 --> 27:27.000
Fine.

27:27.680 --> 27:29.400
I can take you there.

27:29.930 --> 27:30.820
But remember,

27:31.700 --> 27:33.000
you owe me a favor.

27:40.590 --> 27:42.500
I can’t go near you,

27:42.530 --> 27:43.850
but you can't come down either.

27:43.870 --> 27:45.120
Any movement here

27:45.500 --> 27:47.100
will alert the Fox Clan sooner or later.

27:47.400 --> 27:49.250
Once Chang Mei arrives, you'll still die.

27:49.700 --> 27:51.170
But you don't seem worried.

27:52.090 --> 27:53.650
Unless your target...

27:54.240 --> 27:55.940
wasn’t me from the beginning.

27:57.500 --> 27:58.260
Fan Yue.

28:11.030 --> 28:11.890
He...

28:11.940 --> 28:12.920
is seeing an illusion?

28:20.790 --> 28:22.550
This tree has such power.

28:40.200 --> 28:42.450
Who could have thought Jingyou Mountain is hiding such a secret?

28:42.650 --> 28:44.890
This Emotion Tree can create illusions,

28:44.910 --> 28:46.430
devour and kill.

28:46.460 --> 28:47.790
I could make use of it to kill someone on my behalf.

28:47.810 --> 28:49.250
Besides getting rid of Fan Yue,

28:49.270 --> 28:51.280
it's probably best to also destroy this Emotion Tree.

28:51.430 --> 28:53.330
It would definitely be considered as a merit.

29:02.540 --> 29:03.750
He had such a good opportunity,

29:03.780 --> 29:05.790
but Chong Zhao still couldn’t take Bai Shuo away.

29:12.430 --> 29:13.450
Fan Yue!

29:13.740 --> 29:14.810
Stay away!

29:14.920 --> 29:16.110
This is our clan's sacred tree.

29:16.110 --> 29:17.850
Anyone not from the Fox Clan will be attacked if they get near.

29:17.970 --> 29:18.580
Master.

29:18.610 --> 29:19.810
Please release him.

29:20.170 --> 29:21.260
Don't worry.

29:21.350 --> 29:23.250
With his demonic power, he can still hold on.

29:23.270 --> 29:24.560
It's not too late to let him out

29:24.590 --> 29:25.830
after I deal with Fu Ling.

30:00.150 --> 30:04.430
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

30:06.500 --> 30:12.010
♫Because love is thrilling♫

30:11.110 --> 30:12.000
Fan Yue!

30:12.440 --> 30:14.040
Wake up!

30:12.650 --> 30:16.150
♫If you tear open my heart♫

30:16.950 --> 30:19.260
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

30:19.810 --> 30:24.130
♫This pain will gradually fade♫

30:26.870 --> 30:30.600
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

30:29.080 --> 30:29.840
Fan Yue.

30:29.860 --> 30:31.420
Aren't you the Demon King of the Polar Region?

30:30.940 --> 30:33.520
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

30:31.450 --> 30:32.400
If you don't wake up,

30:32.430 --> 30:34.250
I am going to die here with you!

30:33.640 --> 30:35.580
♫I want to tear apart♫

30:35.670 --> 30:36.820
Fan Yue!

30:36.610 --> 30:39.270
♫This sky for you♫

30:39.890 --> 30:42.740
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

30:43.050 --> 30:46.860
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

30:47.090 --> 30:49.160
♫Even if I'll perish♫

30:49.320 --> 30:52.110
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

30:52.280 --> 30:55.130
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

30:55.420 --> 31:03.770
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

31:02.640 --> 31:03.500
How are you?

31:04.110 --> 31:05.410
It's not serious.

31:05.440 --> 31:06.270
What about you?

31:06.530 --> 31:07.370
Don't worry.

31:08.050 --> 31:08.970
If you want to die,

31:09.950 --> 31:11.950
I will definitely die before you.

31:18.210 --> 31:19.200
How dare this Emotion Tree

31:19.200 --> 31:20.550
covet my power?

31:21.080 --> 31:22.510
I merely took advantage of the situation

31:22.510 --> 31:23.840
to investigate what's inside.

31:23.860 --> 31:25.490
Now, we can destroy it

31:25.810 --> 31:26.810
to prevent future troubles.

31:28.490 --> 31:30.570
The Emotion Tree is the foundation of Jingyou Mountain.

31:30.590 --> 31:31.550
If it is destroyed,

31:31.580 --> 31:33.570
I'm afraid Chang Mei won't give up easily.

31:33.770 --> 31:35.570
By then, let alone the Weak Water Stone,

31:35.590 --> 31:36.980
it'll be difficult to even leave safely.

31:38.950 --> 31:41.360
This is indeed the place I saw.

31:41.640 --> 31:43.760
You were also swallowed by the Emotion Tree.

31:43.950 --> 31:45.990
The image from the Contemplation Stone has been fulfiled.

31:46.020 --> 31:47.590
But why did nothing happen?

31:50.770 --> 31:51.480
Be careful.

31:56.670 --> 31:58.000
It's not a physical entity.

31:58.020 --> 31:59.060
It should be a Tree Spirit.

31:59.490 --> 32:00.350
It doesn't have enough power,

32:00.350 --> 32:01.400
hence it doesn't possess a physical form.

32:05.120 --> 32:06.550
It should be caused by your blood.

32:27.020 --> 32:29.790
My people's years of cultivation

32:30.050 --> 32:32.130
have been destroyed in your hands.

32:33.050 --> 32:35.600
You people from Cold Spring Palace are really bold.

32:36.570 --> 32:37.980
You and my master

32:38.000 --> 32:40.070
have known each other for years.

32:40.280 --> 32:41.520
Today, everything I have done

32:41.540 --> 32:43.220
was targeted at Fan Yue.

32:43.250 --> 32:45.080
If you kill

32:45.110 --> 32:46.190
me here,

32:46.720 --> 32:48.110
aren't you afraid that my master

32:48.130 --> 32:49.340
will come and hold you accountable?

32:50.170 --> 32:52.550
You're trying to threaten me with Zhen Yu?

32:52.650 --> 32:55.180
Then let him come and collect your body himself.

33:20.440 --> 33:23.150
The Emotion Tree has been revived?

33:32.400 --> 33:33.440
Human blood?

33:34.090 --> 33:35.920
Is it because of Bai Shuo's blood?

33:38.640 --> 33:39.590
Tree Spirit?

33:40.280 --> 33:41.400
How is that possible?

33:42.260 --> 33:44.380
It's an Emotion Tree that eats people.

33:44.500 --> 33:45.780
Every plant has its own soul,

33:46.170 --> 33:47.640
just like bird and animals.

33:48.090 --> 33:49.240
Through virtue

33:49.810 --> 33:51.120
and years of cultivation,

33:51.290 --> 33:52.740
it has attained consciousness.

33:53.810 --> 33:55.210
If it is not righteous,

33:55.310 --> 33:57.290
gaining enlightenment by consuming human blood

33:57.430 --> 33:58.500
is the evil path.

33:58.770 --> 34:00.400
Even if the Emotion Tree has cultivated its spirit form,

34:00.610 --> 34:02.210
it's probably something evil.

34:02.370 --> 34:04.570
It shouldn't be the human form we saw last night.

34:05.130 --> 34:05.930
Wait.

34:06.620 --> 34:08.020
I used to think

34:08.050 --> 34:09.530
Cang Shan and Tian Huo are about the same age.

34:09.550 --> 34:11.070
But according to what you said,

34:11.250 --> 34:13.040
the real nature of Cang Shan is a stone.

34:13.080 --> 34:14.070
That means he must have been cultivating for

34:14.070 --> 34:15.679
thousands of years in order to achieve a human form.

34:15.710 --> 34:17.280
So, he's not even from the same generation as Tian Huo?

34:17.280 --> 34:18.960
Bai Shuo, don't talk nonsense if you don't know anything.

34:19.150 --> 34:20.239
I'm from the Stone Race.

34:20.280 --> 34:21.940
I was born with a human form.

34:21.969 --> 34:23.570
It's different from the plants cultivating into a spirit form.

34:23.840 --> 34:25.420
I'm about the same age as Tian Huo.

34:25.889 --> 34:27.139
We are still young.

34:27.440 --> 34:29.400
Why do you care so much about age?

34:29.429 --> 34:31.219
That's not the point.

34:31.590 --> 34:32.429
Right now,

34:32.460 --> 34:33.310
this Emotion Tree on Jingyou Mountain

34:33.360 --> 34:34.670
is hiding too many secrets.

34:34.690 --> 34:36.540
When I was swallowed by the Emotion Tree,

34:36.570 --> 34:38.820
I sensed a body under its roots.

34:39.000 --> 34:41.510
There's spiritual energy emanating from the body.

34:41.639 --> 34:42.739
It must have been a demon when it was alive.

34:43.389 --> 34:44.469
Now the tree

34:44.489 --> 34:46.190
has drained its spiritual energy and will wither soon.

34:46.239 --> 34:48.520
Maybe, this tree has already died many years ago.

34:48.710 --> 34:51.060
All these years, it has managed to stay alive

34:51.170 --> 34:52.300
by devouring living things

34:52.330 --> 34:53.250
and absorbing their spiritual energy.

34:53.429 --> 34:54.650
In that case,

34:55.290 --> 34:57.190
could the illusion you saw

34:57.370 --> 35:00.100
be resentment left by the body under the tree,

35:00.310 --> 35:01.760
just like Rong Xian's?

35:05.200 --> 35:06.200
I think...

35:06.740 --> 35:08.210
I know who he is.

35:28.330 --> 35:31.340
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

35:32.090 --> 35:35.590
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

35:35.760 --> 35:39.230
♫I remember that word of concern♫

35:36.920 --> 35:38.330
-Don't need.
-Don’t move.

35:38.760 --> 35:40.240
Chang Mei's last blow

35:39.750 --> 35:43.010
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

35:40.260 --> 35:41.700
contains poison.

35:41.950 --> 35:42.950
If we don't remove the residual poison,

35:42.970 --> 35:44.150
it won't heal even with medicine.

35:43.580 --> 35:46.360
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

35:44.260 --> 35:46.620
Outside, the Fox Clan's soldiers are searching everywhere.

35:46.640 --> 35:47.870
The more you're hurt,

35:47.160 --> 35:50.420
♫It dried in the wind♫

35:48.080 --> 35:49.600
the more danger you're in.

35:51.010 --> 35:52.810
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

35:53.280 --> 35:56.940
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

35:57.650 --> 36:00.980
♫That year, that year♫

36:01.910 --> 36:05.020
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

36:05.460 --> 36:08.900
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

36:09.960 --> 36:12.370
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

36:13.150 --> 36:16.410
♫That year, that year♫

36:17.240 --> 36:20.260
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

36:20.900 --> 36:23.930
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

36:23.780 --> 36:25.590
I didn't find the right opportunity tonight.

36:25.150 --> 36:27.050
♫Layer after layer♫

36:25.690 --> 36:26.690
As for Bai Shuo,

36:26.710 --> 36:27.940
I'll think of another way.

36:28.320 --> 36:31.560
♫Another year passed♫

36:29.930 --> 36:31.480
Why are you looking at me like that?

36:33.300 --> 36:35.240
Are you explaining to me?

36:35.560 --> 36:36.840
Turns out,

36:36.880 --> 36:38.510
you do care about what I think after all.

36:39.440 --> 36:40.440
You misunderstood.

36:41.190 --> 36:43.180
It was your plan to trap Fan Yue.

36:43.540 --> 36:45.880
You're the one who risked your life.

36:44.140 --> 36:47.460
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

36:46.410 --> 36:47.720
I'm saying this

36:47.750 --> 36:49.230
simply to give you an explanation.

36:47.980 --> 36:50.480
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

36:49.250 --> 36:50.040
I don't believe that

36:50.540 --> 36:52.460
I was the only one who was exposed tonight.

36:50.930 --> 36:55.230
♫I remember that word of concern♫

36:52.610 --> 36:54.960
You could have stayed in the shadows and let me die.

36:54.980 --> 36:57.310
But you took Chang Mei's blow for me.

36:55.710 --> 36:59.010
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

36:57.340 --> 36:58.860
Yet, you say that you have no feelings for me.

36:59.520 --> 37:02.270
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

37:02.490 --> 37:03.630
If you die,

37:03.190 --> 37:06.520
♫It dried in the wind♫

37:03.970 --> 37:05.140
it's not good for the mission.

37:05.160 --> 37:06.920
Stop using the mission as an excuse.

37:07.090 --> 37:08.790
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

37:07.130 --> 37:09.250
Bai Shuo brought Chang Mei to the Emotion Tree

37:09.180 --> 37:12.870
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

37:09.280 --> 37:11.170
because she clearly knows that I've trapped Fan Yue inside.

37:11.200 --> 37:12.550
If you were devoted to the mission,

37:12.570 --> 37:14.120
why would you tell her so?

37:13.910 --> 37:17.300
♫That year, that year♫

37:17.160 --> 37:18.310
Chong Zhao,

37:17.880 --> 37:21.000
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

37:18.420 --> 37:20.260
I'll give you one last chance.

37:20.780 --> 37:22.010
What do you really think

37:21.630 --> 37:25.060
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

37:22.040 --> 37:23.570
of Bai Shuo?

37:23.770 --> 37:24.960
Tell me the truth.

37:25.950 --> 37:28.410
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

37:27.400 --> 37:29.390
What does it take for you to trust me?

37:29.070 --> 37:32.550
♫That year, that year♫

37:30.020 --> 37:31.150
Ever since Ning'an City,

37:31.180 --> 37:32.660
I've never hurt you.

37:32.760 --> 37:34.870
Even though I know you aren't sincere about joining Cold Spring Palace,

37:32.960 --> 37:36.220
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

37:34.890 --> 37:36.410
I've never betrayed you.

37:36.750 --> 37:40.230
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

37:36.840 --> 37:37.990
Jingyou Mountain

37:38.010 --> 37:39.010
is full of danger.

37:39.040 --> 37:40.870
We can only rely on each other.

37:40.890 --> 37:42.250
Bai Shuo is on Fan Yue’s side.

37:41.320 --> 37:43.900
♫Layer after layer♫

37:42.280 --> 37:43.240
She won't help you anymore.

37:43.260 --> 37:44.490
Don't you understand?

37:44.550 --> 37:47.540
♫Another year passed♫

37:46.510 --> 37:48.430
Don't let me down again.

37:50.250 --> 37:51.010
Let go.

37:52.640 --> 37:55.440
♫Another year passed♫

38:12.730 --> 38:13.650
Fu Ling.

38:14.110 --> 38:15.110
Listen.

38:15.860 --> 38:17.890
I only love Bai Shuo.

38:23.440 --> 38:24.440
Apart from

38:25.480 --> 38:27.330
saving you that one time at Ning'an City,

38:27.350 --> 38:28.660
I've never done anything else for you.

38:31.160 --> 38:33.520
You don't have to save me again and again.

38:33.550 --> 38:34.730
Stop talking.

38:33.940 --> 38:37.540
♫That year, that year♫

38:34.960 --> 38:35.920
I don't want to hear it.

38:37.920 --> 38:41.100
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

38:38.840 --> 38:40.190
Chang Mei ordered all the entire Fox Clan

38:40.190 --> 38:41.770
to search for us.

38:41.710 --> 38:45.060
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

38:41.960 --> 38:43.870
You'll die if you stay any longer.

38:44.090 --> 38:45.330
Get out of here while you can.

38:45.620 --> 38:46.890
If Zhen Yu asks,

38:45.980 --> 38:48.910
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

38:46.920 --> 38:48.030
just tell him that I'm solely responsible

38:48.030 --> 38:49.190
for the mission's failure.

38:49.110 --> 38:52.870
♫That year, that year♫

38:49.640 --> 38:51.030
It has nothing to do with you.

38:51.760 --> 38:52.810
What about you?

38:53.080 --> 38:56.580
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

38:53.200 --> 38:54.570
If Bai Shuo goes to Cold Spring Palace,

38:54.630 --> 38:55.840
she'll definitely die.

38:56.420 --> 38:57.530
After Uncle Bai died,

38:57.010 --> 39:00.360
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

38:58.510 --> 39:00.460
I'm her only family

39:00.530 --> 39:01.880
left in this world.

39:01.240 --> 39:04.300
♫Layer after layer♫

39:03.170 --> 39:05.390
I promised Uncle Bai to protect her forever,

39:04.760 --> 39:08.650
♫Another year passed♫

39:06.150 --> 39:07.480
even if I die.

39:09.450 --> 39:11.590
I must fulfil my promise,

39:11.820 --> 39:13.430
regardless of whether she still trusts me or not,

39:12.080 --> 39:16.060
♫Another year passed♫

39:26.550 --> 39:28.190
If indeed Chang Mei has formed an alliance with Fan Yue,

39:28.210 --> 39:29.590
Chong Zhao will be

39:29.620 --> 39:30.820
surrounded by tough enemies

39:30.840 --> 39:32.510
in Jingyou Mountain.

39:32.540 --> 39:33.750
There's no way he can bring

39:33.770 --> 39:35.580
Bai Shuo back all on his own.

39:35.610 --> 39:36.480
Grand Master,

39:36.540 --> 39:37.900
I ask that

39:37.930 --> 39:38.820
we go together.

39:45.940 --> 39:48.020
Do you care about Chong Zhao that much?

39:49.230 --> 39:50.510
So much so that

39:51.040 --> 39:51.890
you want to

39:51.920 --> 39:53.200
disobey my order?

39:53.980 --> 39:55.460
I just feel that

39:55.490 --> 39:57.160
since we're all working for you,

39:57.380 --> 39:58.380
we should

39:58.410 --> 39:59.410
take care of each other.

39:59.940 --> 40:00.790
Take care of each other?

40:01.920 --> 40:03.730
Why didn't I realize that

40:04.170 --> 40:06.250
you are this caring and loyal?

40:06.860 --> 40:08.610
You may say you're taking care of him today.

40:08.670 --> 40:09.920
Who knows if, someday,

40:09.940 --> 40:11.650
you will betray me

40:11.960 --> 40:13.400
for him?

40:14.900 --> 40:15.900
I dare not.

40:15.930 --> 40:17.050
If it weren't for you, Grand Master,

40:17.070 --> 40:18.360
I would have been dead.

40:18.800 --> 40:19.920
Grand Master, you've given me

40:19.940 --> 40:21.190
a second chance at life.

40:21.220 --> 40:22.410
I will never betray you

40:22.440 --> 40:23.320
because of anyone.

40:30.580 --> 40:31.670
You know

40:32.780 --> 40:34.740
I hate disloyal people the most.

40:36.150 --> 40:37.430
The bonds of family, friendship, and love

40:37.710 --> 40:38.630
are nothing but

40:38.630 --> 40:39.800
transient fantasies in this world.

40:40.400 --> 40:41.500
Those who gave birth to you

40:42.070 --> 40:44.440
hated you for being weak and sick,

40:45.090 --> 40:46.220
and abandoned you

40:46.250 --> 40:47.440
in the wilderness.

40:48.230 --> 40:49.380
It was me

40:49.470 --> 40:50.430
who took pity on you.

40:51.020 --> 40:53.020
I brought you back to Cold Spring Palace

40:53.050 --> 40:54.370
and raised you.

40:55.810 --> 40:57.000
You were born useless.

40:57.070 --> 40:58.190
You couldn't transform

40:58.190 --> 40:59.580
or cultivate.

40:59.610 --> 41:00.920
It's all thanks to

41:00.940 --> 41:02.640
my efforts that

41:02.990 --> 41:04.070
you have become

41:04.100 --> 41:05.540
the person you are today.

41:06.440 --> 41:08.450
I didn't invest so much in you

41:08.650 --> 41:10.510
only for you to become

41:10.640 --> 41:12.430
a lovesick fool.

41:12.450 --> 41:13.380
Do you understand?

41:13.580 --> 41:14.970
I will remember

41:15.660 --> 41:16.520
all of your words

41:16.680 --> 41:17.960
deep in my heart.

41:20.930 --> 41:22.060
Rise.

41:25.320 --> 41:26.550
You...

41:26.890 --> 41:28.030
shall go with Chong Zhao.

41:30.110 --> 41:32.000
But remember,

41:32.780 --> 41:33.570
there's a price

41:33.600 --> 41:34.770
to pay for everything.

41:35.560 --> 41:36.870
If you can't

41:38.030 --> 41:40.920
keep an eye on him and bring Bai Shuo back this time,

41:43.630 --> 41:44.800
then

41:45.420 --> 41:47.770
return me the life

41:48.480 --> 41:50.350
I gave you.

41:51.770 --> 41:52.670
Yes.

42:02.260 --> 42:05.130
You want to protect her with your life,

42:05.990 --> 42:08.480
but I also will protect you with my life.

42:11.070 --> 42:12.170
Chong Zhao.

42:12.390 --> 42:13.740
This world

42:14.350 --> 42:15.850
is a funny place.

42:46.510 --> 42:47.450
Wu.

42:47.620 --> 42:48.750
You're slacking off again.

42:49.070 --> 42:50.460
Ling Long will punish you

42:50.650 --> 42:51.830
when she returns later.

42:54.710 --> 42:55.460
Who?

42:57.700 --> 42:58.850
Who's there?

43:01.780 --> 43:02.660
Wu.

43:05.850 --> 43:07.450
How could you forget about me?

43:08.070 --> 43:09.040
Qi?

43:12.060 --> 43:12.970
Qi!

43:14.810 --> 43:15.650
Qi!

43:16.520 --> 43:18.000
Okay, I got it.

43:18.020 --> 43:19.490
You may leave if there's nothing else.

43:19.880 --> 43:20.670
-Yes.
-Yes.

43:27.250 --> 43:28.170
Ba.

43:30.310 --> 43:31.660
Ms. Bai, what did you call me?

43:32.050 --> 43:32.930
Ba.

43:33.410 --> 43:34.660
Isn't that you?

43:35.110 --> 43:37.520
I once entered Rong Xian's realm of resentment.

43:37.550 --> 43:39.520
I saw what happened a thousand years ago.

43:39.980 --> 43:41.670
I happen to recognize that Master

43:41.700 --> 43:44.050
is the sister of Saintess Linglong, Wu.

43:44.070 --> 43:45.740
Wu had two guards who followed

43:45.760 --> 43:46.760
her closely,

43:46.780 --> 43:48.250
namely Qi and Ba.

43:48.600 --> 43:50.710
Qi and Wu fell in love.

43:50.740 --> 43:52.220
Now that we're in Jingyou Mountain,

43:52.240 --> 43:54.860
I didn't sense that Master was in a relationship with anyone.

43:55.100 --> 43:56.070
On the contrary,

43:56.070 --> 43:57.750
the grumpy guard Ba

43:57.930 --> 44:00.100
must be one of the two Elders.

44:00.130 --> 44:01.040
At first,

44:01.060 --> 44:02.630
I thought it was Elder Chang Sheng.

44:02.780 --> 44:03.970
But he denied it.

44:04.000 --> 44:05.040
You have a warm and

44:05.060 --> 44:06.500
welcoming disposition.

44:06.530 --> 44:08.300
Had I not witnessed Master's exceptional trust in you

44:08.320 --> 44:10.950
in the strange forest last night,

44:10.980 --> 44:12.630
I wouldn't dare make such a guess.

44:13.060 --> 44:13.790
Master.

44:14.490 --> 44:15.780
Let me stay with you.

44:15.810 --> 44:16.630
It's okay.

44:16.880 --> 44:17.730
Just go.

44:18.230 --> 44:18.880
Yes.

44:23.470 --> 44:24.740
It's been so long.

44:25.050 --> 44:26.240
Who would have thought

44:26.440 --> 44:27.960
someone like you would know about this.

44:28.400 --> 44:29.560
No one has

44:29.800 --> 44:30.970
called me by this name

44:31.310 --> 44:32.430
for many years.

44:34.650 --> 44:36.380
A thousand years is indeed a long time.

44:36.690 --> 44:38.370
The old members of the Fox Clan from back then

44:38.390 --> 44:40.670
have long since perished in that tragedy.

44:42.390 --> 44:43.840
I've previously heard that

44:44.400 --> 44:45.730
death is not scary.

44:46.670 --> 44:47.960
What's scary is that

44:47.960 --> 44:49.630
the last person who remembers you

44:49.630 --> 44:50.710
will also die,

44:51.140 --> 44:52.440
and there will be no trace left

44:52.460 --> 44:54.390
of the deceased's existence.

44:56.670 --> 44:59.320
Even if you almost forgot your name,

44:59.730 --> 45:01.200
you must still remember

45:01.220 --> 45:02.590
your brother.

45:07.830 --> 45:10.240
Is the body under the Emotion Tree

45:10.460 --> 45:11.670
that of Qi?

45:13.230 --> 45:14.550
How do you know?
